<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>While the Amazon.com "itemLookup" api method allows a CSV list of up to 10 ids for the ItemId parameter, itemLookup() ignores multiple results, returning only an item only when $items-&gt;length == 1.</p>

<p>Amazon's API documentation describe the value of ItemId as the "Product IDs":   <a href="http://docs.amazonwebservices.com/AWSEcommerceService/2005-10-05/ApiReference/ItemLookupOperation.html">http://docs.amazonwebservices.com/AWSEcommerceServâ€¦</a></p>

